{
  "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
  "voice": "zh-CN-XiaoxiaoNeural",
  "voice_key": "xiaoxiao",
  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.37,
      "size": 37872,
      "text": "三条边都是整数的直角三角形，最出名的就是三、四、五。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.01,
      "size": 32112,
      "text": "三的平方加四的平方，正好等于五的平方，严丝合缝。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "像这样满足勾股定理的整数三元组，我们就叫它勾股数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "concept-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/concept-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.92,
      "size": 46656,
      "text": "勾股数是一组正整数 a、b、c，满足 a²加 b²等于 c²。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "concept-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/concept-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 43920,
      "text": "除了三四五，还有五、十二、十三，八、十五、十七，都是它的成员。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "concept-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/concept-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.35,
      "size": 37584,
      "text": "问题来了：这样的整数三角形，究竟有多少组，又该怎样一网打尽？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-1",
      "filename": "formula-form-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/formula-form-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "古希腊的欧几里得给出了答案：取两个正整数 m 大于 n。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-2",
      "filename": "formula-form-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/formula-form-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.86,
      "size": 45792,
      "text": "令 a 等于 m²减 n²，b 等于二 m n，c 等于 m²加 n²。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "formula",
      "line_id": "form-3",
      "filename": "formula-form-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/formula-form-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.64,
      "size": 42192,
      "text": "代进去一算，a²加 b²恰好等于 c²，源源不断地造出勾股数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "primitive",
      "line_id": "prim-1",
      "filename": "primitive-prim-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/primitive-prim-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.75,
      "size": 44064,
      "text": "当 m 和 n 互质，而且一奇一偶时，得到的是本原勾股数，三边再无公因数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "primitive",
      "line_id": "prim-2",
      "filename": "primitive-prim-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/primitive-prim-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.84,
      "size": 45504,
      "text": "把一组本原解同时乘以二、乘以三，就得到六八十、九十二十七这些派生解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.51,
      "size": 40176,
      "text": "调大斜边的上限，屏幕上的整数点会越来越多，铺成放射状的图案。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "点开任意一组，看看它的平方和是不是真的严丝合缝。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.36,
      "size": 37728,
      "text": "勾股数是满足 a²加 b²等于 c²的整数三元组。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "欧几里得公式用 m、n 两个参数，把它们全部生成出来。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "pythagorean-triples",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/pythagorean-triples/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "一条古老的定理，藏着无穷的整数之美，我们下次再见！"
    }
  ],
